des: "Great low-calorie meal perfect for lunch or a quick snack. Garnish tacos with lettuce, tomatoes, black olives, cilantro, or garnish of choice."
ins: Place chicken in a bowl and season with chili powder, cumin, and garlic powder. Spoon chicken into taco shells. Pour Buffalo wing sauce over seasoned chicken and top with blue cheese.
